House Resolution 990
By: Representatives Dempsey of the 13th, Lumsden of the 12th, and Barton of the 5th
A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending the 2025 Awards of Honor recipient, Dave Roberson; and for
2 other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Dave comes from a family of public servants and he was recently re-elected to
4 his second term as Sheriff of Floyd County, where he has 30 years of continuous service; and
5 WHEREAS, Dave is a certified jail officer, peace officer, general instructor and crisis
6 intervention training instructor through the Georgia Peace Officers Standards and Training
7 Council; and
8 WHEREAS, Dave is a recipient of the 2022 Georgia Department of Community Supervision
9 Public Stakeholder Award, a 2018 Greater Rome Convention and Visitors Bureau Superstar
10 of Service, and the 2005 Field Services Deputy of the Year; and
11 WHEREAS, Dave serves on the Board of Directors of Community Criminal Justice
12 Foundation, Sexual Assault Center of NWGA, Harbor House Child Advocacy Center, Blood
13 Assurance Rome, and Vital Grace; and
