14 WHEREAS, Dave serves his community through his volunteerism with Rome, Georgia,
15 Cares Disaster Relief Efforts, Rome-Floyd Parks and Recreation Challenger Baseball and
16 Basketball Leagues, as well as the Special Olympics of Georgia; and
17 WHEREAS, Dave is a member of the Coosa Valley Fraternal Order of Police, Walk to End
18 Alzheimer's, Noon Optimist Club, Exchange Club of Rome, and an Advisory Board Member
19 of NextDoor at Living Proof Recovery; and
20 WHEREAS, Dave is a graduate of Leadership Rome Class of XXXVI, a past mentor for the
21 Rome Middle School Habitudes Program, a Contestant 2017 Rome Celebrity Dance
22 Challenge, and participates in the Floyd County Sheriff's Office Community Programs:
23 Sheriff Santa, Santa for Seniors, and F.R.E.E.D.; anf
24 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the outstanding accomplishments of this
25 remarkable and distinguished Georgian be appropriately recognized.
26 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
27 the members of this body recognize Dave Roberson for his outstanding dedication to the
28 community, commend him as a recipient of the 2025 Heart of the Community Awards Honor
29 Recipient, and extend the most sincere best wishes for continued success.
30 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
31 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Dave
32 Roberson.
